{"type": "article", "id": 27343, "title": "模仿日式庭院的沙发", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-26T06:58:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 65, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702162501h1kcfU2idGweDWY5.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.claessonkoivistorune.se/\">Claesson Koivisto Rune</a> 最近参考了日式美学为意大利家居品牌 <a href=\"http://www.arflex.it/\">Arflex</a> 设计了这个名为 Bonsai 的沙发系列，线条优美的造型很容易使人联想到日式庭院中那些大小不一、精心修剪成云朵状的灌木丛。搭配木质的平台后，很像是日本住宅内的凹间（床の間），可以在上面添加灯具或者是装饰品，营造出一种特别的室内风格。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021624586CERTDUhpiAbFdtL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.44865526\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162459oGVJCnxdLy3F7Ogr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51344743\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162500sKe1O4T8nlZc7mUw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162500C1l5UjI7nM48VqEP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}